These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, july, august
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, dancing, puzzles
House: victorian, cottage, gothic-revival, modern
City: liverpool, berlin, colone, boston
4 different games are played: go, whist, chess, snooker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, amaryllis, aconite
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, cat, ferret
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
 5. the cottage house is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is the person playing whist##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the victorian house##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing chess##1
13. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
14. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's birthday is in august##1
15. the person who growsaconite is the gothic-revival house##1
16. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the victorian house##1
17. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | june       | august      | july       | february    |
| Hobby         | board-games    | puzzles    | cooking      | dancing    |
| House           | modern | victorian       | gothic-revival | cottage     |
| City   | liverpool         | colone  | boston      | berlin     |
| Game   | whist          | snooker     | chess       | go |
| Flower         | amaryllis       | dahlia | aconite       | daisy   |
| Pet     | ferret     | cat  | chinchilla         | hamster   |

