.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, bongani, alhambra, cain
City: hamburg, london, hannover, miami
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, electrician, photographer, chef
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, domino, go
House: farmhouse, palace, wooden, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, coral, blue, lilac
 1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 2. the palace house is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person playing go is the electrician##1
 6. the electrician is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the photographer is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the right of the mechanic##1
12. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
14. the person who likes white is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
16. the person who likes white is on the left of the photographer##1
17. the townhouse house is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| Cigar          | alhambra     | bongani     | fonseca      | cain  |
